            "label": "Which of the following best describes your situation? (If none of these apply you are not eligible for modified independent status)",
            "optionsLabelPosition": "right",
            "inline": false,
            "tableView": false,
            "values": [
                {
                    "label": "There is an irreconcilable rift between me and my parent(s), and I can provide satisfactory evidence of a severe and permanent breakdown in the relationship between you and your parent(s) that has existed for at least one year unless a sudden and serious situation has occurred.",
                    "value": "irreconcilableRift",
                    "shortcut": ""
                },
                {
                    "label": "You would normally be classified as a dependant student by StudentAid BC, but you are unable to contact or locate your parents, step-parent, sponsor, or legal guardian due to conflict or emergency (such as war, famine or natural disaster) in the country where they live.",
